          "material": "## 材料\n\n求解二次方程的方法：\n\n使用求根公式：$x = \\frac{-b \\pm \\sqrt{b^2 - 4ac}}{2a}$\n\n```python\ndef solve_quadratic(a, b, c):\n    discriminant = b**2 - 4*a*c\n    if discriminant >= 0:\n        x1 = (-b + discriminant**0.5) / (2*a)\n        x2 = (-b - discriminant**0.5) / (2*a)\n        return x1, x2\n    else:\n        return None\n```",
